<P>
   BC-JACOBY-COLUMN-BOS (k), by Jeff Jacoby, concerns a local topic
and will not move today.
</P>
<P>
   &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &UR; The Boston Globe &LR;  &QL;
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
