<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Marilyn Geewax's Business Commentary: Futurists banking on
 &HT;    `coming matriarchy'
 &HT;    By Marilyn Geewax
 &HT;    c. 1998 Cox News Service
