<HEADLINE>
&HT;        WITHOUT OPPONENT, SHUSTER'S CAMPAIGN STILL KICKING
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;     By Paul Kane  
 &HT;    c. 1998 States News Service  
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON, July 25 -- While he was busy negotiating the final
pieces of the more than $200 billion highway bill, Rep. Bud
