u v &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-FEATURE-BUDGET-ART-BO     07-27 0777
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-FEATURE-BUDGET-ART-BOS </SLUG>
  
 ART ADV.: A graphic with EARTH-IMPACT and a map with
AUTHOR-MULLONEY are being transmitted to NYT Photo Service
subscribers.  
