<P>
   BRODY-HEALTH (Undated) _ The Personal Health column: New
evidence strongly suggests that it is time to add triglycerides to
cholesterol and homocysteine as substances in the blood that
influence your chances of developing heart disease. How to stay on
top of this substance. By Jane E. Brody. (``l'' code)
