<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-07-27 16:49 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4845 &Cx1f; taf-z
u l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BRODY-HEALTH-ART-NYT &LR;      07-27 1197
