<P>
   NTERNATIONAL
</P>
<P>
   PALESTINIANS-COKE _ WEST BANK, _ A Palestinian bottler who won a
Coca-Cola Co. bottling franchise the West Bank in Gaza calls it a
``major event for palestine,'' and added that it signals a trend
toward American companies doing business directly with Palestinains
instead of going through Israeli companies _ something the Clinton
administration has been pushing. (Kaplow, Cox News Service).
</P>
