   &UR; THE WAR MOVIE TO END WAR MOVIES &LR;
</P>
<P>
   ``Some say this war movie is too realistic,'' writes  &UR; Jim &LR; 
 &UR; Mullen  &LR; of Entertainment Weekly about ``Saving Private Ryan.''
``But so far everyone who's seen it has lived.''
</P>
<P>
   Nonetheless,  &UR; J.M. &LR;  said it was the first time in memory that he
